variable.name: nsrr_id
variable.description: National Sleep Research Resource (NSRR) participant ID key
variable.comment: The NSRR subject IDs permit linking of CHS participant data to NSRR data. Interested researchers may visit the NSRR web site and sign-up for data access. Users will have to complete online Data Access and Use Agreement forms when seeking access to data on the site. Datasets with corresponding data in dbGaP will be noted on the NSRR web site.
